Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.50,0:25:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,其他辅祭并没有涉案吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Have you ruled out the involvement of any of the other altar boys?{\r}
