Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.72,0:25:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,被警方追捕\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}down under McCormick Place,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.05,0:25:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,几乎被驶过的火车辗死\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}but not before he was almost killed by a passing train.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.43,0:25:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,马丁魏尔事务所\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Law office of Martin Vail.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.27,0:25:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,他来了会跟你联络\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}He's gonna call you as soon as he gets in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.19,0:25:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,知道了 我保证 谢谢\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I know. I promise you. Okay, thank you very much.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.44,0:25:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 娜欧蜜! - 在\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- Naomi! - Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.98,0:25:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,待会再说\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- Talk to you later. Bye. - Hey.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.15,0:25:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,抱歉 有新的委托人\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Sorry I'm late. We have a new client.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.03,0:25:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 我就怕你这么说 - 是谁?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- I was afraid you were gonna say that. - Who?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.11,0:25:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,大家叫他什么?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}You know what they're calling him already?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.45,0:25:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 圣马可小屠夫 - 我喜欢\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- The Butcher Boy of Saint Mike's. - I like that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.03,0:25:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,以后还会有别的叫法\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Well, that's good. You're gonna be hearing it a lot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.66,0:25:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,砍死主教的小子是新委托人?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}This kid who chopped up the Archbishop, he's our new client?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.83,0:25:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,汤米 你得试着\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Tommy, you're gonna have to try harder{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.29,0:25:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,加上"涉嫌" 两个字\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}to get the word "allegedly" into your vocabulary,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.54,0:25:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 如果你还想当律师 - 你的咖啡\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- especially if you want to be a lawyer. - Here you go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.21,0:25:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 汤米 咖啡? - 不 谢了\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- Tommy, you want coffee? - No. No, thanks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.05,0:25:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,他案发时在场\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}All right. He admits he was in the room when the killing occurred,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.30,0:25:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,但什么都没看到\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}but he didn't actually see it happen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.26,0:25:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 我可以打岔吗? - 不行\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- Can I stop you right there? - No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.59,0:25:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,他去还书给主教\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}He was returning a book to the Archbishop.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.97,0:26:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,睡房有声音\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}He heard loud noises in the bedroom.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.97,0:26:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,他进去看到影子\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}He went in. He sees a figure,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.48,0:26:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,有人在尸体上方 他失去知觉\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}someone in the shadows kneeling over the body. He blacks out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.56,0:26:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,接下来就发现\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Next thing he knows,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.86,0:26:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,醒来时警笛在响 他满身是血\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}sirens are screaming, he's covered in blood.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.03,0:26:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,警察在铁路隧道找到他\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}The cops find him in a train tunnel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.19,0:26:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,在他口袋发现主教的戒指\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}He's got the Archbishop's ring in his pocket.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.57,0:26:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,他偷走主教的戒指?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}He stole the Archbishop's ring?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.95,0:26:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我只是说戒指在他口袋\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I didn't say that. I said it was in his pocket.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.62,0:26:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,就这样?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Is that it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.83,0:26:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,对\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Yep.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.96,0:26:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,乱七八糟 马提\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}That's... That's bullshit, Marty.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.72,0:26:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我没听过这么逊的故事\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}That's the worst bullshit story I've ever heard in my entire life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.68,0:26:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,这是我们的故事 开始干活吧\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Now it's our bullshit story. Okay, let's get to work.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.77,0:26:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,重要的是动机\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Now, the name of the game here is motive,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.02,0:26:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,而控方找不到嫌犯的杀人动机\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}as in, the prosecution doesn't have one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.02,0:26:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我们只要\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}So what we have to do here{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.52,0:26:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,证明可能有其他凶手\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}is prove that someone else could have committed the crime.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.65,0:26:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,这就是合理的疑点\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Then we can establish reasonable doubt.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.65,0:26:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,查出罗主教的底细\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}So I want to know everything I can about this guy, everything he was into.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.53,0:27:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,去数据库 去找市政资料 国税局档案\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}We go to database, go to Hall of Records, IRS files.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.83,0:27:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 甚至所谓的慈善组织 - 所谓?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- Even his so-called charities. - So-called?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.20,0:27:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,他可是个主教\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}The guy was a priest, for Christ's sake.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.37,0:27:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,抄下来 B-32.156\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Naomi, write this down. B-32.156.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.50,0:27:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,刻在主教胸口\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}That was carved into the Archbishop's chest.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.34,0:27:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 涉嫌而已 - 不\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- Allegedly. - No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.09,0:27:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,这次是真的 不过谢谢提醒\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}That was a fact, but I appreciate the effort, Tommy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.88,0:27:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,别客气\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Thanks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.39,0:27:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我要持刀谋杀 毁尸\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I also need case histories on murder by stabbing,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.72,0:27:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,宗教谋杀案的记录\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}murder by mutilation, murder by religion.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.68,0:27:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 我还要精神科医师 - 你早就需要\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- Also, I'm gonna need a psychiatrist. - You're telling me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.56,0:27:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,别找法庭医师\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}And not the kind that lives in a witness box, either.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.81,0:27:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我要执业医师\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I need a real one this time,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.40,0:27:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,他得熟知失忆症\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}and someone who knows about amnesia.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.94,0:27:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 他长得什么样子? - 那个小屠夫?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- What does he look like in person? - The Butcher Boy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.53,0:27:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,像个男童军\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Like a Boy Scout.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.41,0:27:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,得过雕刻奖章的男童军\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}A Boy Scout with a merit badge in carving.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.70,0:27:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,主教和萧先生是好友\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}The Archbishop was a close personal friend of Mr. Shaughnessy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.96,0:27:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,他今早过来问我这里谁最好\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}He came to me earlier this morning and asked me who was my best man,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.71,0:27:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 我说是你 - 谢了\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- I said you. - Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.42,0:28:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,萧先生 如果要我起诉此案\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I trust, Mr. Shaughnessy, if I am to prosecute this case,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.80,0:28:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,那我必须获得完全的授权\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I'll be given the authority which comes with the assignment.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.18,0:28:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,案子是你在办 不过我先说清楚\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}You're the one trying the case, but let's establish one thing at the outset.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.77,0:28:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我要死刑\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I want the death penalty.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.02,0:28:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我得先熟悉此案\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I'd like an opportunity to go over the case{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.85,0:28:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,才能做出决定\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}before we make a determination{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.19,0:28:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,到底要不要死刑\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}on whether or not to seek the death penalty.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.77,0:28:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,尽管发表意见 珍娜\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I'm open to anything you have to say, Janet,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.61,0:28:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,不过没得商量\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}but in my mind there's no debate.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.86,0:28:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,那个男孩怎么说?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Did he say anything, the boy they picked up?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.78,0:28:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,不是他干的\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Yeah. He didn't do it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.54,0:28:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,这案子稳赢 珍娜\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}It's a slam dunk, Janet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.37,0:28:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,谢谢你的信心\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Excuse me. I appreciate your faith in me,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.87,0:28:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我也不想争论...\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}and I don't mean to be argumentative...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.29,0:28:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,争论是你的职业\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Hey, that's what we pay you for.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.92,0:28:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,...若是证据确凿就不需要我了\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}...but if it's as open and shut as you say it is, then you don't need me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.92,0:28:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,公设律师不会辩护 让法官决定得了\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}The P.D. will plead no contest, throw the kid on the mercy of the court.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.64,0:28:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 没有公设律师 - 他这么快就有律师? 是谁?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- There's not a public defender. - He's got a lawyer already? Who?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.19,0:28:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我是马丁·魏尔  史坦勒的律师\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Hey, I'm Martin Vail. I'm defending Aaron Stampler.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.15,0:29:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 我得查看现场 - 小屠夫 对吧?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- I need to inspect the murder site. - The Butcher Boy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.49,0:29:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,对 我也忘了他的名字\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Thank you. Yes. I forgot his real name.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.50,0:29:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,怎么? 信心动摇了?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}What's the matter, Marty, lost your faith?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.38,0:29:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,需要宗教慰藉?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Looking for a little religion?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.96,0:29:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,告诉我  法律顾问\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Now tell me, Counselor,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.17,0:29:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,到底是谁想出风头?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}which one of us is the true headline-chaser here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.34,0:29:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 和你不同 我是被指派接手此案 - 你行吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- Unlike you, I was assigned to this case. - Yeah? Think you're up to it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.26,0:29:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,书的版权卖了吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Sell the book rights yet, or are you gonna wait a while?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.51,0:29:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,想看照片吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Want to see some pictures?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.19,0:29:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,挺有意思的\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Come on. They're kind of cute.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.07,0:29:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,这种暴行简直是惨绝人寰\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I think you'll agree they clearly show the heinous nature of the crime.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.20,0:29:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,小小意见\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}A small piece of advice,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.16,0:29:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我建议你在庭上别说"惨绝人寰"\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}don't use the word "heinous" in a courtroom.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.66,0:29:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,陪审团大部分人听不懂\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Half the jury won't know what you're talking about.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.83,0:29:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,小小意见\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}One small piece of advice,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.42,0:30:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我建议你别期待我当你助手\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I'm not sitting second chair to you anymore.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.88,0:30:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,你不知道我早毕业吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}In case you hadn't noticed, I graduated.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.59,0:30:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 我没有理由离开 - 理由多了\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- I had no reason to leave. - You had every reason to leave.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.39,0:30:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,你怎能再做下去?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}How can you still work for them?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.56,0:30:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,你要我跟随你的脚步 马提?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}What? You really expect me to trot out after you, Marty?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.19,0:30:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,为了你而辞职? 我不要名贵房车\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Quit, just because you did? I don't need a Mercedes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.23,0:30:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,也不必上晚间新闻\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I don't need to see my face on the evening news.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.62,0:30:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,你知道我会来的 是吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}You knew I was coming here, didn't you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.74,0:30:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,你知道我会替他辩护 所以你接手这案子\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}You knew I would defend him. That's why you took the case.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.37,0:30:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,求萧纳西把案子给你 是吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}You asked Shaughnessy for this, didn't you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.66,0:30:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,拜托\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Oh, please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.17,0:30:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,怎么? 马提 你紧张了?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}What's the matter, Marty, you nervous?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.88,0:30:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,很久没碰上聪明的女人?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Been a while since you rubbed up against a woman with a brain?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.26,0:30:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,怎么? 你呢? 良心不安 辗转难眠?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}What is the matter? You tired? You haven't been sleeping well?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.60,0:30:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,你才有心病\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}You're the one with the score to settle, Marty.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.89,0:30:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我睡得很好\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I sleep great at night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.01,0:31:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 嗨 - 嘿\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- Hi. - Hey.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.99,0:31:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,(库克郡惩戒部)
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.13,0:32:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,谢谢\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Thanks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.05,0:32:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 他在哪儿? - 这里\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- Hey. Where is he? - Over here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.03,0:32:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我们会坐在一起\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}All right, we'll be sitting at a table together,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.86,0:32:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,还有我两个搭档  控诉后\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}along with two of my associates. Now, once the charges are read,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.32,0:32:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,法官会问你如何答辩\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}the judge is gonna ask you how you plead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.04,0:32:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 没有罪 - 不行\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- Not guilty. - No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.41,0:32:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 可是我没有罪 魏尔先生 - 我不管 这无关紧要\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- But I'm not guilty, Mr. Vail. - I don't care. It doesn't matter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.29,0:32:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,你闭上嘴 什么都别说\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}You can keep your mouth shut. You don't say anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.25,0:32:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,你得说我没有罪\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Well, you're going to say I'm not guilty.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.92,0:32:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,别管我说什么\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I'll say whatever I say. You don't have to worry about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.80,0:32:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 可是 魏尔先生... - 我就是这意思\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- But, Mr. Vail... - This is exactly what I'm talking about.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.84,0:32:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,你不能插嘴 你最好要习惯\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}This can't go on in the courtroom, so you might as well get used to it now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.89,0:32:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,让我说话 你什么都别说\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I speak. You do not speak.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.72,0:32:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,你只要装作无辜\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Your job is just to sit there and look innocent.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.68,0:33:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我是无辜的\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Well, I am innocent.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.56,0:33:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,没错! 就是这表情\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}That's it! That's exactly how I want you to look.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.65,0:33:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,这样就对了 记得吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}That's exactly it. Now, can you remember that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.73,0:33:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,去照照镜子 记住这表情\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Look in the mirror if you have to. That's the look.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.86,0:33:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,不必 我就是这模样\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I don't have to. This is how I always look.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.07,0:33:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,你已经占了优势 是吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Well, then you're way ahead of the game already, aren't you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.07,0:33:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,别笑\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Don't smile.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.08,0:33:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,别这样\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Don't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.21,0:33:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,魏尔先生 你要发表声明吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Mr. Vail, can we have a statement?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.67,0:33:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,不 我们要找出真相\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}No. We're gonna find out what happened here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.17,0:33:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,面对巨大压力你如何为艾伦辩护?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}How can you defend Aaron Stampler in the face of all this public pressure?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.97,0:33:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,唯一的压力是寻求真相\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}The only pressure is to find the truth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.34,0:33:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,...他的手沾满主教的血\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}...with the Archbishop's blood on him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.76,0:33:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,你又找警方谈吗? 我叫你别这样做\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}You've been talking to the police again, haven't you? I told you not to.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.31,0:33:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,他们通常都大错特错\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}As usual, they get everything wrong.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.72,0:33:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,那你怎么解释\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Come on. How're you gonna explain{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.85,0:33:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,他满身都是血的事实?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}the fact that he had blood-soaked clothing on him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.52,0:33:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 我们都砍刀了 - 在这节骨眼\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- We all saw that. - At this juncture,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.77,0:33:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我不必解释\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I'm not going to explain it at all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.94,0:33:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我刚受理此案\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I've only recently been retained in this case.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.02,0:33:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,重要证据仍然有疑点\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Significant facts are in dispute here and continue to be in dispute.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.69,0:33:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,马提 你的拿手把戏是揭被害人疮疤\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Marty, you're a master at putting the victim on trial{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.49,0:33:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,来打官司\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}to help your own client.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.86,0:33:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,此案会有点困难\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}That's going to be very difficult in this case.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.08,0:34:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,受害人是我的委托人\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}A victim in this case is my client.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.04,0:34:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,只有两名受害人 没有嫌犯\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}We have two victims here, no suspects. Thank you very much.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.96,0:34:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,你担心他的安危吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Are you worried about his safety, Marty?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.12,0:34:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,不会\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}No. Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.81,0:34:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,没什么大不了\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}It's not a case.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.14,0:34:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我相信判决将不容置疑\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I don't think there'll be any question about the verdict.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.44,0:34:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,请起立\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}All rise.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.07,0:34:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,午安 各位\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Good afternoon, ladies and gentlemen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.66,0:34:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 法警? - 控方起诉艾伦·史坦勒\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- Bailiff? - State v. Aaron Stampler.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.79,0:34:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,双方都在吗? 请坐 双方都在吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Is everyone here? Sit down. Is everyone here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.12,0:34:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,都在 庭上\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Yes, Your Honor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.17,0:34:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,检察官?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Madam Prosecutor?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.83,0:34:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,控方起诉犯人艾伦史·坦勒\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}The State charges the prisoner, Aaron Stampler,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.29,0:34:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,一级谋杀罪名\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}with the crime of murder in the first degree.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.84,0:34:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,你的委托人如何答辩?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}How does your client plead, Counselor?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.63,0:34:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,庭上 可以的话\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Your Honor, if it pleases the court,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.84,0:35:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,在对他提出起诉前\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I need time to make a complete psychiatric evaluation{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.18,0:35:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我必须为他做心理评估\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}before any charges are brought against us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.35,0:35:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,控方有充足证据提出起诉\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}State has more than enough evidence to warrant the allegations, Your Honor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.10,0:35:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我同意 动议不准\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I agree. Motion denied.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.98,0:35:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,史先生\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Mr. Stampler,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.85,0:35:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,你了解对你的控告吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}do you understand the charges brought against you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.86,0:35:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 了解... - 庭上\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- Yes. Yes, I... - Your Honor, I direct my client{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.19,0:35:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我指示他不予回答\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}not to answer that question{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.40,0:35:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,他的答覆可能对自己不利\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}on the grounds that his response may tend to incriminate him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.70,0:35:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,被告不愿表明\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}The defendant is taking the Fifth{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.86,0:35:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,他是否了解控诉?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}on whether or not he understands the charges?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.70,0:35:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,是的 在进行完整心理评估前\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Yes, Your Honor. Until we have a complete psychological evaluation,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.33,0:35:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,他将对所有的问题保持缄默\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}he will be taking the Fifth on any and all questions posed to him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.04,0:35:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,州政府控告艾波案有前例\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}State v. Appleby for your review of precedent.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.84,0:35:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,请你参考\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.56,0:35:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,不行 我不行\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}No, no, I can't do that. No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.69,0:35:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,你想要什么?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}What do you want?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.24,0:36:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我在找史艾伦住的房间\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I'm looking for the room a kid named Aaron Stampler stayed in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.95,0:36:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 你是警察? - 我是他叔叔\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- You the police? - I'm his uncle.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.23,0:37:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 谢谢 - 嘿\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- Thanks. - Well, hey.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.99,0:37:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 这是阿力的 - 他是谁?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- This is Alex's. - Who's Alex?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.99,0:37:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 他是另一个辅祭 - 辅祭?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- He's one of the other altar boys. - An altar boy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.33,0:37:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,辅祭会戴这玩意?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}An altar boy was wearing this?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.17,0:37:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,望弥撒时不戴\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Well, not at the mass.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.17,0:37:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,他攻击我的同事\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Well, this altar boy attacked a colleague of mine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.50,0:37:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,他伤得很重\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}He hurt him pretty bad.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.51,0:37:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,他在你房间干嘛?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}What do you think he was doing there in your room?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.60,0:37:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 我房间? - 对\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- My room? - Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.85,0:37:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,不晓得 我...\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I can't... I don't know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.56,0:38:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 我什么都没有 - 到哪儿找得到他?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- I mean, I don't have nothing. - You know where I could find him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.82,0:38:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,谁? 阿力?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Who? Alex?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.49,0:38:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 我不晓得 - 是吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- No, I don't... I don't know where he is. - You don't?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.87,0:38:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 琳达是谁? - 琳达?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- Who's Linda? - Linda?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.71,0:38:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,你女友吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}She your girlfriend?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.05,0:38:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 她在哪儿? 我要找她谈 - 我不知道\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- Where is she? I'd like to talk to her. - I don't know where she is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.68,0:38:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,你好像瞒着我什么 艾伦\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Why is it that I get this feeling you're not telling me something, Aaron?{\r}
