Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.99,0:39:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我不晓得有谁会干这事 魏尔先生\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I don't know who's capable of such a thing, Mr. Vail.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.42,0:39:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 谢了 - 不客气\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- Thanks. - Sure.{\r}
