Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.22,0:39:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,你要我查出\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}And you want me to look into this amnesia question{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.81,0:39:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 他究竟记得什么 - 对\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- and see what he actually knows. - Yeah.{\r}
