Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.06,0:40:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,失忆症主因是滥服药物 痉挛抽筋\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}The major causes of amnesia are substance abuse, seizures,{\r}
