Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.32,0:40:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我觉得他在说实话\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I think the kid's telling the truth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.70,0:40:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,好的\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Okay.{\r}
