Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.67,0:40:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,老实说 我挺想的\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}In fact, I'm looking forward to it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.09,0:40:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,但是我不会证实他的说词\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}But I won't go in there to validate his story, understood?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.51,0:40:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 你做你的 我做我的 - 没错\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- You do your job, I do mine. - That's right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.26,0:40:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,有必要会做核磁共振造影\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Listen, if I think it's necessary,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.14,0:40:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,电脑断层扫描和精神测验\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I'd want to get an MRI, EEG, and neuropsych testing, agreed?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.89,0:40:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 好的 晚安 大夫 - 晚安\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- Yes, Doctor. Good night, Doctor. - Good night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.02,0:40:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我将进行录影\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I'll be recording our meetings for Mr. Vail,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.44,0:40:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,所以不能保密\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}so what we talk about isn't as confidential the way it might be{\r}
