Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.37,0:41:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 不必 我很了解 - 很好\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- No, ma'am. I understand. - Good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.67,0:41:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 好吧 应该没问题 - 好\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- So, okay. I think we'll be fine. - All right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.13,0:41:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 待会再见 - 好吧\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- I'll see you later. All right. - Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.13,0:41:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,再见\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Bye.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.18,0:41:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,魏先生说主教死后\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Mr. Vail told me that there was a period of time{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.39,0:41:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,有段时间你曾失去记忆\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}surrounding the Archbishop's death that you don't remember.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.52,0:41:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 对吗? - 没错 我失去时间\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- Is that right? - Yeah. Yes. I lost the time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.28,0:41:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我是指昏过去\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I mean, I blacked out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.07,0:41:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 你以前曾经这样吗? - 有过\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- Have you had these blackouts before? - Yes. Yes, I have.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.91,0:41:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,第一次是什么时候?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}When's the first time you remember them happening?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.92,0:41:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,从我十二岁开始 我猜\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}They started when I was about 12, maybe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.13,0:41:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,你父母知道吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Were your parents aware of what was happening to you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.92,0:41:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,不知道 我母亲死了\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}No. My mother was dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.05,0:42:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,你父亲呢?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}And your father?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.43,0:42:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,他不是好人\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}No. No. No. He was not a nice man.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.44,0:42:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 你曾接受治疗吗? - 什么?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- Did you seek treatment? - Did I what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.28,0:42:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,你看过医生吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Did you see a doctor for them?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.36,0:42:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,没有\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}No. No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.41,0:42:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,在乡下只有跌断脚才看医生\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}You don't go see a doctor in Creekside unless your leg's broke.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.17,0:42:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 可以谈谈吗? - 说吧\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- Hey. Can I talk to you? - Talk.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.09,0:42:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 我马上带她回来 - 我算什么?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- Excuse us. I'll bring her right back. - How dare you. What am I?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.97,0:42:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,随你摆布的棋子?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I'm some kind of chess piece you can just move around?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.10,0:42:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 我正在吃饭 - 你们何时摊牌?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- I was in the middle of my lunch. - When are we getting all the discovery?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.73,0:42:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,你想干嘛?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}What do you want, Marty?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.85,0:42:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我想知道 当我摊牌时\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I want to know when we're getting all the discovery.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.44,0:42:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 我要提出动议 - 才怪\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- I've got motions to file. - No, you don't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.48,0:42:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,你只想谈条件\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}You're looking to make a deal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.32,0:42:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我没这权力\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I have no authority to deal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.86,0:43:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我还没和委托人谈过 你呢?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I haven't discussed this with my client. What's your excuse?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.66,0:43:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,如果要谈条件\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Well, if I thought we needed to make a deal,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.79,0:43:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我有充分授权\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I have all the authority I want.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.29,0:43:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,胡扯! 萧纳西只是在利用你\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Bullshit! Shaughnessy wants the whole shot on this,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.46,0:43:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,达到目的\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}and he's using you to get it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.46,0:43:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,你应该让他认罪\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Anybody in your position would deal this down{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.21,0:43:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,不判死刑\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}to murder with no death penalty.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.42,0:43:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,才怪 我对这件案子很有把握\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}My position? We have a fucking great case.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.76,0:43:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,有把握?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Great case?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.63,0:43:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,没前科 没证人 没认罪 没动机\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Lack of prior record, no eyewitness, no confession, no motive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.51,0:43:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,铁证如山\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Hard evidence.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.14,0:43:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,可惜你不会以精神失常辩护\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I assume this conversation means you're not going with insanity,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.52,0:43:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我的心理医生会把他拆穿\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}which is a shame. My shrinks would have torn him apart.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.77,0:43:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,你让他保持缄默很高明\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}By the way, your pleading the Fifth on the charges was brilliant.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.78,0:43:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 不错吧? - 是\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- It was good, wasn't it? - Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.49,0:43:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我很满意\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I liked it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.20,0:43:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,败诉你会倒霉 不是萧纳西\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}You lose this case, you take the fall, not Shaughnessy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.83,0:43:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 跟我合作 - 我们要上法庭\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- Talk to me. - We're going to trial, Marty.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.46,0:43:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,好吧\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}All right, all it takes is one,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.42,0:43:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,总有陪审团员会同情他\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}just one juror that doesn't believe he did it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.21,0:43:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,特别是有孩子的陪审员 只要看到这孩子的脸...\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}One juror, with a kid his age, looks into that face...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.92,0:44:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,我得承认他装得很像 是你叫他这么做的?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}I've got to admit, that face is great. Are you prepping him to take the stand?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.14,0:44:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,他口吃的样子还真像回事\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}That stutter, it's priceless.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.06,0:44:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,马提 别说你相信不是他干的\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Marty, don't tell me you think he didn't do it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.19,0:44:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,小艾伦让你心软吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}What, has little Aaron Stampler gotten to you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.44,0:44:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,你们要判他死刑 不只是坐牢\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}We're not just talking about jail here. It's about ending someone's life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.07,0:44:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,如果你们错了\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}If you're wrong and Shaughnessy's made you do this,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.07,0:44:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 你会心安吗? - 当然会\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- you gonna be able to live with it? - I'll live.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.95,0:44:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,法庭上见\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}See you in court.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.58,0:44:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,庭上 我们承认这是谋杀\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Your Honor, we stipulate that murder was done here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.55,0:44:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,因此不需要展示照片\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}Therefore, these photographs have no remaining probative value.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.92,0:44:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,不只是谋杀 这也是毁尸及虐尸\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}This is not just murder. This is a case of mutilation and torture.{\r}
