Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.10,0:44:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,- 让人触目心惊 - 异议 庭上\N{\fntahoma\fs11\1c&H00FFFF&}- is shock appeal. - That is not true, Your Honor.{\r}
